quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,91,Amene apanga Buku la Korani kukhala magawo awiri
  15,92,"Kotero, pali Ambuye wako, tidzawafunsa"
  15,93,Pa zonse zimene anali kuchita
  15,94,"Motero lalikira poyera zonse zimene walamulidwa, ndipo choka pakati pa osakhulupirira"
  15,95,Ndithudi Ife tidzakuteteza kwa onyoza
  15,96,Iwo amene amatumikira mulungu wina kuonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni iwowo adzadziwa
  15,97,Ndithudi Ife tilikudziwakutizimakupweteka mumtima mwako zinthu zimene amanena
  15,98,Motero lemekeza Ambuye wako ndipo khala mmodzi wa iwo amene amagwada pomulemekeza Iye
  15,99,Ndipo pembedza Ambuye wako mpaka pamene ola lotsimikizidwa likupeza
  16,1,"Chiweruzo cha Mulungu chidzabwera, ndipo kotero musachifulumizitse. Kulemekezeka ndi kuyamikidwa kukhale kwa Iye kuposa zonse zimene akumufanizira"
  16,2,"Iyeamatsitsaangelondimawuakeamalamulokwaakapolo ake amene wawafuna ndikuwauza kuti muwachenjeze iwo kuti, “Kulibe Mulungu wina koma Ine ndekha. Kotero ndiopeni Ine.”"
  16,3,Iye adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi mwachoonadi. Iye akhale kutali ndi zimene akumufanizira nazo
  16,4,Iye ndiye adalenga munthu kuchokera ku dontho la umuna ndi la ukazi ndipo taonani iye amatsutsa poyera
  16,5,Iye adakulengerani nyama ndipo mu izo mumapeza zofunda ndi zithandizo zina ndiponso nyamazo mumadya
  16,6,Ndipo mumanyadira pamene mumazisaka kudza nazo ku nyumba kwanu madzulo ndi pamene mumapita nazo kuubusa kukazidyetsa m’mawa